name: Trey Mangum
content:
#BlacKkKlansman (full thoughts coming soon, but some highlights): 

• Overall a good film though at least 30 minutes could have been cut. 
• It’s a clear Spike Lee film through and through. 
• Star-making for John David Washington. Excellent here.
• Laura Harrier was miscast.
